item.title: GRAPES.jl - GRAph Prediction of Earthquake Shaking in Julia (Version 1.0.0)
item.description: Abstract GRAPES.jl is a Julia-language code for earthquake early warning. GRAPES.jl implements the GRAph Prediction of Earthquake Shaking (GRAPES) algorithm using graph neural networks. The GRAPES.jl package provides code for EEW ground motion predictions. Access Points https://code.usgs.gov/esc/grapes.jl/-/tree/1.0.0/
